MediaPipe (mp) - AI-Based Hand & Face Tracking
ðŸ”¹ What is it?
MediaPipe is a Google AI library for real-time hand tracking, face detection, pose estimation, and object tracking.

ðŸ”¹ Uses:
âœ… Hand Tracking â€“ Detects and tracks hand gestures without gloves
âœ… Face Recognition & Pose Detection â€“ Identifies faces and human body movements
âœ… Object Detection â€“ Tracks objects like pens, balls, or tools
